    "We report an order of magnitude speedups in Section 5.4.",
    "We comprehensively evaluate all proposed quantitative judges on both absolute rating and relative preference datasets.",
    "The quantitative judges consistently outperform their base judges.",
    "They can also outperform fine-tuning of the base judges on both quality and computational efficiency at the same time; and outperform an order of magnitude larger judge and specialized judges on quality.",
    "These results are complemented with additional studies on key components of our design."
